definitions.definition: Any of the predatory amphibious reptiles of the family Crocodylidae ; ( loosely ) a crocodilian , any species of the order Crocodilia , which also includes the alligators , caimans and gavials .
A long line or procession of people (especially children) walking together.
A fallacious dilemma , mythically supposed to have been first used by a crocodile.
